4HEvwQ2qVnw.title: SIDEMEN CHARITY MATCH 2025 [OFFICIAL STREAM]
4HEvwQ2qVnw.description:
Sidemen Charity Match 2025

Donate here: https://www.sidemenfc.com 

On the 8th of March Sidemen FC and YouTube Allstars are coming together to play the 2025 Charity Match at Wembley Stadium.

Use the hashtag #SDMNCharityMatch to talk about the game!

OFFICIAL STREAM starts at 2:10pm GMT

Kick off time is at 3pm GMT

The Sidemen Charity Match 2025 is in aid of the following charities and funds raised will be split as follows:

Bright Side 43%
BBC Children in Need 50%
M7 Education 7%

We will also donate all of the profit we make through the match and related activities to the following charities:

Bright Side 86%
M7 Education 14%

Any donations you make are greatly appreciated and going to great causes! We hope you enjoy the match.

For full details and terms and conditions please visit https://sidemenfc.com.

Viewers of this livestream are strictly prohibited from re-streaming or rebroadcasting this content on any platform. Any unauthorised re-streaming will result in the immediate removal of the infringing livestream and a copyright strike issued to the violator.

HeZO_LcQALI.title: SIDEMEN CHARITY MATCH 2023 [OFFICIAL STREAM]
HeZO_LcQALI.description:
Sidemen Charity Match 2023

Donate here: https://www.sidemenfc.com 

On the 9th of September Sidemen FC and YouTube Allstars are coming together to play the 2023 Charity Match at London Stadium.

Use the hashtag #SDMNCharityMatch to talk about the game!

OFFICIAL STREAM starts at 2:15pm BST

Kick off time is at 3pm BST

The Sidemen Charity Match 2023 is in aid of the following charities:

Brightside: https://www.brightside.charity
CALM: https://www.thecalmzone.net/what-we-do
Teenage Cancer Trust: https://www.teenagecancertrust.org/about-us
Rays of Sunshine Children's Charity: https://raysofsunshine.org.uk
m7 Education: https://www.m7education.org.uk

Any donations you make are greatly appreciated and going to great causes! Hope you enjoy the match.

Funds raised today will be split between the five charities the Sidemen Charity Match 2023 is in aid of: 37.5% to BRIGHTSIDE, 25% to CALM, 25% to Teenage Cancer Trust, 7.5% to Rays Of Sunshine and 5% to M7 Education.

For full details and terms and conditions please visit SidemenFC.com.

On the 24th of September Sidemen FC and YouTube Allstars will come together to play the 2022 Charity Match at The Valley, Charlton.

For full details and terms and conditions please visit SidemenFC.com.

• Jme: http://www.twitter.com/JmeBBK

Rules:

The player claims one box at the start of the game, without its contents being revealed. The contestant then chooses the other boxes, one at a time, to be opened and removed from play. Throughout the game, the player is offered an amount of money to quit, being asked, "Deal or no deal?" If the contestant rejects every deal and eliminates all the other boxes, the player keeps the money that was in their original case or box. The contestant "wins" depending on whether the player should have taken one of the deals or should have held onto the original case or box until the very end.
